{"tid":1623741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有狗家人响天水圍誤人子弟","createTime":"2019-10-05T01:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T07:36:21.000Z","uid":263438,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"316ddd6944bdfce02860ed7f6a5471fa616b288d","tid":1623741,"uid":263438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rj9JBpB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frj9JBpB.jpg&h=d620e36e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vi58Nwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvi58Nwi.jpg&h=0b43554f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警仆街就係人都知<br />\n價值觀有問題<br />\n佢屋企人竟然教小學！<br />\n好驚佢散播不良資訊，不正確價值觀，誤人子弟呀！<br />\n救救小朋友！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bv0XFR9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbv0XFR9.png&h=dc57083f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qesosaps.edu.hk/teacher?lightbox=dataItem-jlg9n8xz1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qesosaps.edu.hk%2Fteacher%3Flightbox%3DdataItem-jlg9n8xz1&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=0f209f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qesosaps.edu.hk/teacher?lightbox=dataItem-jlg9n8xz1</a><br />\n莊的媛老師<br />\n小學曾讀九龍塘國際學校，後來返回本地小學讀<br />\n2012-2014 嶺南大學持續進修學院 教育心理學高級文憑<br />\n2014-2016 城市大學心理學學士<br />\n2017-2019 浸會大學教育學系教育文憑（小學英文）<br />\n2017-2018 伊利沙伯中學舊生會小學做TA<br />\n2018-2019 同一間學校做老師<br />\n威水史：讀書嗰陣最叻抹黑，扮可憐，賊喊捉賊<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/woodychong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwoodychong&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=465b7187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/woodychong</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/chong_woody?igshid=18co1zukdm8ct\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fchong_woody%3Figshid%3D18co1zukdm8ct&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=2da11c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/chong_woody?igshid=18co1zukdm8ct</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaOVsAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaOVsAR.png&h=4986f86f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/he1oBub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhe1oBub.jpg&h=07f3a2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救救小朋友！"},{"pid":"8c9a7226307940d2388cb2e6f5c350b3d86725b2","tid":1623741,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42bddd30e6dc37c69a7eb8e8deaca908d6f29823","tid":1623741,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>相由心生</strong></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c819a05b6b86491989e436bad0b828474bfe15ca","tid":1623741,"uid":263438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"記得一人一信去伊小關注下事情呀"},{"pid":"e73a01d9ad3394fade5bdab27773c9196d6114c9","tid":1623741,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028a9f85343eac4ef011a1863517d248d5d31eec","tid":1623741,"uid":263438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73a01d9ad3394fade5bdab27773c9196d6114c9","tid":1623741,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:18:23.000Z","msg":"多謝提供資料"},{"pid":"578c47791e50af927be44e056bd58554e54a03d0","ti